<keyLead id="3425959F5F36521AFF10FB2DFBF01449" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">
8. Elytra longer, more than 0.8 times as long as pronotum (
<bibRefCitation id="EB454B5B5F36521AFCA9FB2DFC4015F4" author="ASSING V" box="[779,909,1191,1212]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127" pagination="1269 - 1283" refId="ref5974" refString="ASSING V. (2009): New species and additional records of Lathrobium and Tetartopeus from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 41 (2): 1269 - 1283." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
: figure 25).: posterior margin of sternite VIII without median incision (
<bibRefCitation id="EB454B5B5F36521AFC85FB34FC61159B" author="ASSING V" box="[807,940,1214,1235]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127" pagination="1269 - 1283" refId="ref5974" refString="ASSING V. (2009): New species and additional records of Lathrobium and Tetartopeus from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 41 (2): 1269 - 1283." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
: figure 26); ventral process of aedeagus basally stouter, straight and apically obliquely truncate (
<bibRefCitation id="EB454B5B5F36521AFF7DFB66FEAD1449" author="ASSING V" box="[223,352,1260,1281]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127" pagination="1269 - 1283" refId="ref5974" refString="ASSING V. (2009): New species and additional records of Lathrobium and Tetartopeus from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Linzer Biologische Beitrage 41 (2): 1269 - 1283." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
: figures 26-27). 
<collectingCountry id="F7C3763A5F36521AFE5CFB66FD85144A" box="[510,584,1260,1282]" name="Turkey" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">Turkey</collectingCountry>
: 
<collectingRegion id="4D10F8485F36521AFDF2FB66FD731449" box="[592,702,1260,1281]" country="Turkey" name="Kastamonu" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">Kastamonu</collectingRegion>
............................... 
