<subSubSection id="C7CE65215F36521AFF10FA73FF331701" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127" type="description">
<paragraph id="8F6B36AA5F36521AFF10FA73FF331701" blockId="8.[178,1085,1529,1609]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">
Distribution and natural history: The type locality is situated to the southwest of 
<collectingRegion id="4D10F8485F36521AFEC2F99DFE5F1764" box="[352,402,1559,1580]" country="Turkey" name="Kars" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">Kars</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion id="4D10F8485F36521AFE3FF99DFDE21764" box="[413,559,1558,1580]" country="Turkey" name="Kars" pageId="8" pageNumber="1127">Kars province</collectingRegion>
, northeastern 
